Class WetClean

java.lang.Object

dryclean.cyprusDryCleanEntities.WetClean
All Implemented Interfaces:
CleaningStyle
public class WetClean extends LaundryItem
Represents a wet cleaning laundry item. Wet cleaning total cost is calculated using the quantity, price, water rate, and ironing rate. Extends the LaundryItem class.
